HEADWORD: dock-walloper
<hw>dock-walloper</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a laborer who loads and
unloads vessels in a port.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> stevedore, loader, longshoreman, docker, dockhand,
dock worker, lumper.</syn>⟦br⟧
